{"tid":1956480,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"反送中運動至三月中逾 7,800 人被捕　809 人無條件釋放　近廿人獲撤控","createTime":"2020-04-03T07:58:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T10:04:01.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"28acd4e7f6ef8e63bd76294e4fe4cc731c3efb5e","tid":1956480,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T07:58:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/20200403-0520copy_u3Y0e_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F20200403-0520copy_u3Y0e_1200x0.png&h=ab40fc67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n反送中運動至今近 9 個月，警方回應《立場》查詢時表示，由去年 6 月 9 日至今年 3 月 19 日，警方在「各區示威活動」當中拘捕 7,854 人，年齡介乎 11 歲至 84 歲，已落案控告 1,252 人，當中被控暴動罪有 564 人。被捕人士當中，有 1,376 人未成年，佔整體 17.5%，當中 151 人已被起訴。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，7,854 名被捕人士當中，有 5,870 男 1,984 女，涉及罪名包括參與暴動、非法集結、傷人、襲擊致造成身體傷害、普通襲擊、縱火、刑事毀壞、襲警、阻礙警務人員執行職務、藏有攻擊性武器等。<br />\n<br />\n近 5,800 人案件仍在調查<br />\n<br />\n上述被捕人士當中，有 5,758 人的案件仍在調查中，他們都保釋候查，或者在拒絕續保後獲釋放。至於在警方警誡後釋放，以及無條件釋放人數，分別為 6 人和 809 人。另外，有 1,281 人已經完成或正進行司法程序。<br />\n<br />\n7,854 名被捕人士當中，16 歲以下被捕人數有 547 人，分別有 391 男 156 女，45 人被起訴；18 歲以下被捕人數有 1376 人，分別有 993 男 383 女，有 151 人被起訴。涉及罪名包括參與暴動、非法集結、刑事毀壞、襲警、阻礙警務人員執行職務、藏有攻擊性武器等。<br />\n<br />\n被捕學生逾 3,200<br />\n<br />\n警方又說，被捕人當中 3,219 名為學生，當中 465 人已被起訴。<br />\n<br />\n至於律政司昨日就 2020 - 2021 年開支預算，回應立法會議員的書面回覆就提到，根據保安局提供的資料，自 2019 年 6 月 9 日至 2020 年 2 月 29 日， 警務處就「反修例」事件共拘捕 7,613 人，當中 1,235 人已經或正在進行司法程序。<br />\n<br />\n1,235 名已經或正在進行司法程序的人士當中，78 人須承擔法律後果，包括 52 人被定罪、25 人須簽保守行為，及 1 人被判照顧或保護令，另外有 19 人獲撤銷控罪。其餘人士的司法程序仍在進行中，暫時沒有罪名不成立的個案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%89%E6%9C%88%E4%B8%AD%E9%80%BE-7-800-%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-809-%E4%BA%BA%E7%84%A1%E6%A2%9D%E4%BB%B6%E9%87%8B%E6%94%BE-%E8%BF%91%E5%BB%BF%E4%BA%BA%E7%8D%B2%E6%92%A4%E6%8E%A7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%258B%2595%25E8%2587%25B3%25E4%25B8%2589%25E6%259C%2588%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%2580%25BE-7-800-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-809-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E9%2587%258B%25E6%2594%25BE-%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25BB%25BF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%2592%25A4%25E6%258E%25A7%2F&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2BlcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=4d2712da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%258B%2595%25E8%2587%25B3%25E4%25B8%2589%25E6%259C%2588%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%2580%25BE-7-800-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-809-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E9%2587%258B%25E6%2594%25BE-%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25BB%25BF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%2592%25A4%25E6%258E%25A7%2F&h=4bc32cd9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%89%E6%9C%88%E4%B8%AD%E9%80%BE-7-800-%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-809-%E4%BA%BA%E7%84%A1%E6%A2%9D%E4%BB%B6%E9%87%8B%E6%94%BE-%E8%BF%91%E5%BB%BF%E4%BA%BA%E7%8D%B2%E6%92%A4%E6%8E%A7/</a>"},{"pid":"28dd2bf8b9e32882f9ab914ba6ea818454a12789","tid":1956480,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:02:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8eb3b42507ab52dcdb0eb7fa6ac807b0811ccf75","tid":1956480,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28dd2bf8b9e32882f9ab914ba6ea818454a12789","tid":1956480,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:02:20.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:04:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=